      <title>美国银行称印度卢比贬值增强其套利交易吸引力</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-10/cheaper-rupee-boosting-currency-s-carry-lure-in-em-bofa-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国银行表示，与新兴市场货币相比，印度卢比稳定且价格低廉，成为套利交易者的最爱。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-10/cheaper-rupee-boosting-currency-s-carry-lure-in-em-bofa-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 10 Jun 2024 01:30:00 GMT</pubDate>
