      <pubDate>Mon, 10 Jun 2024 00:45:36 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>伊拉克称将在未来几天内达成协议重启通过土耳其的石油出口</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-10/iraq-says-deal-to-restart-oil-exports-via-turkey-coming-in-days</link>
      <description><![CDATA[欧佩克第二大产油国伊拉克表示，预计将很快与库尔德斯坦半自治地区及当地的国际石油公司达成最终协议，以重启石油出口。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-10/iraq-says-deal-to-restart-oil-exports-via-turkey-coming-in-days</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 10 Jun 2024 00:25:30 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>据《华尔街日报》报道，埃利奥特收购西南航空近 20 亿美元股份</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-10/elliott-takes-almost-2-billion-stake-in-southwest-wsj-reports</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据《华尔街日报》报道，埃利奥特投资管理公司已持有西南航空公司近 20 亿美元的股份，并计划推动这家美国航空公司进行改革。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-10/elliott-takes-almost-2-billion-stake-in-southwest-wsj-reports</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 10 Jun 2024 00:13:16 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>市场关注美联储利率决议，油价在连跌一周后企稳</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-09/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-june-10</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于交易员们关注一系列行业报告和美联储的利率决定，市场仍在消化 OPEC+ 恢复供应的决定，油价在连续一周下跌后趋于稳定。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-09/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-june-10</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 09 Jun 2024 23:34:50 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>马克龙受挫后欧元下跌，东证指数上涨：市场综述</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-09/euro-falls-after-elections-us-stock-futures-steady-market-wrap</link>
      <description><![CDATA[法国总统马克龙在欧洲议会选举后宣布提前投票，欧元跌至近一个月以来的最低点。周五美国公布的强劲就业报告导致亚洲货币下跌。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-09/euro-falls-after-elections-us-stock-futures-steady-market-wrap</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 09 Jun 2024 22:27:15 GMT</pubDate>
